---
title: Harissa Spiced Prawn Tacos with roast baby potatoes
description: Spiced prawns and refreshing fresh veg salsa are the perfect thing to fill up a soft and fluffy tortilla fresh from the oven. A dollop of cooling creme fraiche and a side of spiced baby potatoes rounds out a healthy and taste meal.
